name: TripGuide - Web app Black Friday Deal 2021
description:
TripGuide is the best web app UI kit for travel booking, hotel booking, flight booking, car rentals, and much more. We've included editable files in Figma, Sketch, Adobe XD, which means you can easily customize the designs - change colors, fonts, and icons. TripGuide is a collection of 138 clean & minimal pre-made screens. It's the best tool for travel businesses to promote their business online. Each web app UI design screens is fully responsive, allowing users to access your website from any device.
